<p><b>2</b> GE.09-16220 
</p>
<p> The criminal investigative bodies should coordinate and harmonize their actions so 
as to guarantee their effectiveness. The International Commission against Impunity in 
Guatemala (CICIG) plays a vital role in this area.  
 Finally, it is necessary to adopt a set of legislative reforms, including in respect of 
access to justice. The legislature has a basic responsibility to step up the effort to combat 
impunity in Guatemala. 
</p>
<p> 
</p>
